content.text:
The following shall be considered accessory buildings
or structures for the purposes of this section: tennis courts, paddle
tennis courts and similar facilities without provisions for night
play; swimming pools; garages for passenger or commercial vehicles;
greenhouses; playhouses; garden houses; toolhouses; stables; barns;
solar energy collectors and studios.[Amended 2-7-1984; 5-15-1984; 8-1-1989]
